Definition at line 99 of file container.cpp.

ContainerBasePrivate::const_iterator moveit::task_constructor::ContainerBasePrivate::childByIndex ( int  index,
bool  for_insert = false 
) const

Retrieve iterator into children_ pointing to indexed element. Negative index counts from end, i.e. -1 is last, -2 is second last, etc. (if !for_insert) If for_insert == true, negative indexes are shifted by one: -1 is end(), -2 is –end(), etc. Contrary to std::advance(), iterator limits are considered.
